categories: Category:Military personnel of the Sith Empire

nodes.text: Wicke was a male Human who served as a soldier in the army of the resurgent Sith Empire on the planet Balmorra during the Cold War in 3642 BBY. Stationed in Camp Vigil, he was corrupt, even collaborating with enemies of the Empire like the smuggler that would be later known as Voidhound and the resistance fighter Numen Brock, in exchange for stims.
